# Shell Install Safety

## Script Basics
- Use explicit `install|update|uninstall` branching with clear fallback usage text.
- Quote variable paths in shell commands to avoid path parsing issues.

## Safety
- Do not download and execute external scripts during install.
- Keep uninstall behavior scoped to plugin-owned paths only.

## BT Compatibility
- Use BT-compatible plugin paths under `/www/server/panel/plugin/<name>`.
- Keep icon copy paths aligned with BTPanel static icon directory.
